<categorie type="typeText" name="aboutMe" txt="Who is maxwellito?&lt;br&gt;My real name is Maxime Duluc, I'm a young graduate in computer science also passionate by photography and design. I'm addicted to Adobe softwares, and especially Flash. I love to create on any platform : paint, illustration and webdesign.&lt;br/&gt;I use the main languages : HTML/CSS/JavaScript/PHP/AS3 to make any kind of websites. I work in freelance, don't hesitate to contact me for more information about my services.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:contact@maxwellito.com&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;ContactMe&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;data/_ressources/iconFlickr.png&quot; vspace=&quot;2&quot;/&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.flickr.com/xxsmax&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;/&gt;flickr.com/xxsmax&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;data/_ressources/iconVimeo.png&quot; vspace=&quot;2&quot;/&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.vimeo.com/maxwellito&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;/&gt;vimeo.com/maxwellito&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;data/_ressources/iconRSS.png&quot; vspace=&quot;2&quot;/&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.maxwellito.com/feed&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;/&gt;RSS (maxwellito.com)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;" />

